Format strings and beautify JSON

Formatter by jlodes allows you to use multiple string formatters in the browser as a pop-up or in a stand-alone tab.

This plugin supports two shortcuts:
Open the popup: Ctr+Shift+F (Cmd+Shift+F on Mac)
Open in new tab: Alt+Shift+F

Source code: https://github.com/Silver0034/FormatterByJlodes
